      "type": "entrance",
      "option": 1,
      "citation": "Cf. Ps 17 (16):6, 8",
      "text": "To you I call; for you will surely heed me, O God;\nturn your ear to me; hear my words.\nGuard me as the apple of your eye;\nin the shadow of your wings protect me."
    },
    {
      "type": "communion",
      "option": 1,
      "citation": "Cf. Ps 33 (32):18–19",
      "text": "Behold, the eyes of the Lord are on those who fear him,\nwho hope in his merciful love, to rescue their souls from death,\nto keep them alive in famine."
    },
